snippet.title: FrenVania OST (Official, full soundtrack)
snippet.description:
Hey gamers, wanna listen to the FrenVania soundtrack? Well, you're already doing it :)

Timestamps:
0:00 Intro ~ "Bonfireside Chat"
1:33 Title Screen ~ "Your First (...and only?) Campaign"
3:37 Stage 1 (Entrance) ~ "Vampire Hoonter"
5:41 Stage 2 (Graveyard) ~ "Massive Sand (Graveyard Mix)"
8:01 Stage 3 (Water Cave) ~ "Sinking Too Far"
10:14 Stage 4 (Castle Walls) ~ "Tidal Plant II (Moonlight Remix)"
12:15 Stage 5 (Main Hall) ~ "Bach With Liberties"
14:11 Stage 6 (Clock Tower) ~ "Half Past Perish"
17:49 Boss Battle ~ "Another Wandering Warrior"
21:02 Grand Dead Battle ~ "Ruler of Unity"
24:17 Count Dracula Battle ~ "Menuet for a Final Boss"
28:12 Ending ~ "Running II"

Wanna play FrenVania? You can find it here: https://yaru.itch.io/frenvania
VargFren is a character by Vinesauce Joel: https://www.twitch.tv/Vargskelethor

My games: https://yaru.itch.io/
My twitter: https://twitter.com/GameDevYal

What is a man, but a miserable little pile of secrets? But enough, have at you!
